JoJot is a lightweight note-taking app that ties your notes to your virtual desktops. Switch to a different desktop and JoJot automatically shows the notes you left there — zero friction, always in context.

A few things to get you started:
  &#x2022; Ctrl+T  — open a new tab
  &#x2022; Ctrl+W  — close the current tab
  &#x2022; Closing the window keeps JoJot running in the background — relaunch to get it back.

Feel free to delete this tab once you're ready.</value></data>

